s/00000190-df21-d566-adfa-ff23b2010000</link><description>当一架无人机击中以色列高层建筑时，楼上居民只能孤军奋战：上周胡塞武装袭击特拉维夫，这对一个摩天大楼之国来说是个坏兆头，因为这个国家没有办法保护他们</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/new-fear-unlocked-for-israelis-living-in-high-rises-during-drone-attacks/00000190-df21-d566-adfa-ff23b2010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政界人士认为内塔尼亚胡赞成达成协议，但将避免在国会演讲中这么说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-think-netanyahu-favors-deal-but-will-avoid-saying-so-in-speech/00000190-e3ee-d9bf-a195-e7ee3a6a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡访问期间民主党的回避强化了他和特朗普的说法，因为他们寻求重建关系。尽管所有人的目光都集中在总理的讲话上，但很少有人注意到司法政变的卷土重来</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-think-netanyahu-favors-deal-but-will-avoid-saying-so-in-speech/00000190-e3ee-d9bf-a195-e7ee3a6a0000</guid></item><item><title>一场失败的比赛：加沙战争导致海外球员远离以色列体育遭受干旱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-losing-game-israeli-sports-suffers-drought-as-gaza-war-sees-overseas-players-stay-away/00000190-d515-dbb4-a7d2-df1f92af0000</link><description>运动员不敢与以色列队签约，他们的父母拒绝让他们来，经纪人也要求更多的钱。只有那些已经在以色列打过球的人才准备好本赛季在这里打球——除了财力雄厚的三巨头篮球俱乐部</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-losing-game-israeli-sports-suffers-drought-as-gaza-war-sees-overseas-players-stay-away/00000190-d515-dbb4-a7d2-df1f92af0000</guid></item><item><title>新特拉维夫咖啡馆致力于治愈 10 月 7 日四分五裂的社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/the-new-tel-aviv-cafes-looking-to-heal-communities-torn-apart-on-october-7/00000190-e06f-d566-adfa-eb6f5c910000</link><description>特拉维夫最新的连锁咖啡店 Café Otef 的每家分店均由疏散的基布兹成员经营并配备员工，所有收益都捐献给社区。 “你需要早上醒来并忙碌起来，这就是我们的孩子们现在看到的我们正在做的事情，”负责基布兹雷伊姆分部的罗伊特说</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/the-new-tel-aviv-cafes-looking-to-heal-communities-torn-apart-on-october-7/00000190-e06f-d566-adfa-eb6f5c910000</guid></item><item><title>报告：Nova 节幸存者讲述哈马斯恐怖分子如何在 10 月 7 日强奸他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/report-nova-festival-survivor-recounts-how-hamas-terrorists-raped-him-on-october-7/00000190-e396-dab4-afb9-f3fe6cff0000</link><description>以色列第 12 频道的匿名报道与去年法国报纸发表的报道一样 ■ 详细描述 10 月 7 日强奸案的报道以及营救幸存者和第一时间到达现场的人的证词浮出水面</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:38:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/report-nova-festival-survivor-recounts-how-hamas-terrorists-raped-him-on-october-7/00000190-e396-dab4-afb9-f3fe6cff0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将就伊朗的侵略向国会发出警告。但他的伊朗政策却是一个巨大的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-will-warn-congress-about-the-iranian-threat-his-iran-policy-has-been-disastrous/00000190-e00c-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff06130000</link><description>当以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在国会演讲中提到伊朗时，鉴于他在这个问题上长达数十年的可怕、甚至是灾难性的记录，世界应该将其视为采取完全相反行动的信号</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:50:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-will-warn-congress-about-the-iranian-threat-his-iran-policy-has-been-disastrous/00000190-e00c-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff06130000</guid></item><item><title>“维持现状”：内塔尼亚胡否决了本格维尔，他说犹太人可以在圣殿山祈祷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/jews-can-pray-on-temple-mount-ben-gvir-upends-israeli-policy-while-netanyahu-in-u-s/00000190-e3d4-d548-a3ba-efde61200000</link><description>本-格维尔在议会表示，“政治领导层允许犹太人在敏感地点进行祈祷”；来自联盟和反对派的议员们站出来反对这一声明，称本-格维尔是一个“纵火狂”。总理办公室后来表示“圣殿山的现状没有也不会改变”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/jews-can-pray-on-temple-mount-ben-gvir-upends-israeli-policy-while-netanyahu-in-u-s/00000190-e3d4-d548-a3ba-efde61200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将在人质家属的注视下向国会发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-fear-netanyahus-optimism-over-a-deal-is-to-help-him-survive-u-s-visit/00000190-e153-dbe5-a7fa-f77bccbf0000</link><description>接近以色列总理的消息人士称，他对国会的讲话将是和解的，他将赞扬拜登几十年来对以色列的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-fear-netanyahus-optimism-over-a-deal-is-to-help-him-survive-u-s-visit/00000190-e153-dbe5-a7fa-f77bccbf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列同意撤离250名加沙伤病员前往阿联酋接受治疗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-evacuate-250-sick-and-wounded-gazans-for-medical-treatment-in-uae/00000190-df16-d566-adfa-ff3605d10000</link><description>在高等法院就一项请愿书举行听证会之前，COGAT表示，以色列和世界卫生组织正在计划从埃拉特进行初步医疗后送，该请愿书要求建立一个从加沙疏散伤病员以获得必要医疗护理的系统</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-evacuate-250-sick-and-wounded-gazans-for-medical-treatment-in-uae/00000190-df16-d566-adfa-ff3605d10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对被占领的美国的访问只不过是自恋的政治活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-visit-to-an-otherwise-occupied-america-is-nothing-but-narcissistic-politicking/00000190-e0fb-d566-adfa-ebfb9b150000</link><description>拜登承诺将利用其总统任期的最后几个月来确保加沙停火和人质返回，但即将卸任的总统将拥有多少精力还有待观察 ■ 据与内塔尼亚胡关系密切的人士透露，内塔尼亚胡并没有放弃人质协议 — — 或者与沙特阿拉伯的正常化协议 — — 但如果他确实选择达成协议，他仍然面临严重障碍</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-visit-to-an-otherwise-occupied-america-is-nothing-but-narcissistic-politicking/00000190-e0fb-d566-adfa-ebfb9b150000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在国会演讲中表示，以色列不会重新安置加沙，称校园抗议者是伊朗“有用的白痴”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡向国会发表的讲话中没有提及“协议”或“停火”。 ■ 以色列推迟卡塔尔会谈；官员称，出发等待拜登与内塔尼亚胡就加沙协议进行讨论 ■ 内塔尼亚胡游说白宫和国会向以色列运送美国扣留的重型炸弹 ■ 真主党播放无人机视频，称其显示以色列纵深的以色列国防军空军基地 ■ 以色列国防军称其拦截了两架在以色列境内发射的无人机以色列东部 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在北部受重伤，两人在加沙战斗中受重伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>